sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Server
    participant dB
    User->>Server: Request Data
    activate Server
    note right of Server: Validate Request
    Server->>dB: Query
    activate dB
    dB-->>Server: Result
    deactivate dB
    alt Success
        Server-->>User: 200 OK
    else Error
        Server-->>User: 500 Error
    end
    deactivate Server